===Etymology===
From {{der|zh|sit}}. Cognate with {{cog|bo|རྒྱུ་||to go; to walk; to move; to wander}}, {{cog|lep|ᰚᰪ|tr=yŭ}}, {{cog|raw|yɨ||to flow}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Same word as {{och-l|游|to swim}}. See there for more.

